[{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0102","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0102.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-2920","title":"Joomla! Foobla Suggestions 组件 本地文件包含漏洞","description":"Joomla! 组件 Foobla Suggestions 1.5.1.2 存在目录遍历漏洞（CWE-22），攻击者可通过 index.php 的 controller 参数传入目录遍历序列（如 ../）读取服务器任意文件。该漏洞影响使用该组件的 Joomla! 站点，CVSS 评分 6.8（中危），攻击者无需认证即可远程利用，通过构造恶意 controller 参数实现任意文件读取，可能导致敏感配置文件、源代码泄露。ExploitDB 已收录公开利用代码。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.8,"aliases":["CVE-2010-2920"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-07-30T20:30:03.927","updated":"2026-06-16T23:21:45.433","remediation":"升级或卸载存在漏洞的 Foobla Suggestions (com_foobla_suggestions) 组件 1.5.1.2 版本，或替换为其修复版本（需过滤 controller 参数中的 \"../\" 等目录穿越字符）。若无法立即更新，可在 Joomla! 后台禁用该组件，并通过 .htaccess 添加规则拒绝 index.php 请求中携带 \"controller=../\" 或 NULL 字节等穿越序列，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://packetstormsecurity.org/1004-exploits/joomlafoobla-lfi.txt","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12120","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/39341","http://www.vupen.com/english/advisories/2010/1844","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/57660","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12120","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-2920.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/2010/CVE-2010-2920.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/6bfef5eb290cbfeb2b2cb4d2bae8e5cab0243137/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-2920.yaml","https://github.com/sepehrdaddev/zap-scripts/blob/2b63b02ca79cc7f0023cdbab72c5c6c774354b07/active/CVE-2010-2920.js","https://github.com/0xKayala/Custom-Nuclei-Templates/blob/1940dfd29577590f076c89dec5c30d809d68f210/6001-to-7000-templates/cve-2010-2920-1980.yaml","https://github.com/rix4uni/nucleihub-templates/blob/579a0234551b9e0e322460a62dc77bd6109e4aff/nucleihub-templates/CVE-2010-2920.yaml","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2010-2920_10.yaml","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/d6a37376bba332b033eeef800cc2b5fc0701d843/CVE/data/2010/CVE-2010-2920.json","https://github.com/coreruleset/seaweed-reports/blob/3e2a1bd3dbca1b431f18ed0dabb71fa729d4d059/2022/Nov/13/lfiArtifact/lfiReport.csv","https://github.com/tholian-network/vulnerabilities/blob/cd8798a37e6d58633681c9596bee14e4189ad0e9/database/vulnerability/CVE-2010-2920.json","https://github.com/1in9e/gosint/blob/bdda4461515c4398c08638676bbbfe451b73ff95/client/vuln_scan/nuclei/tools/nuclei-templates/cves/2010/CVE-2010-2920.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0102.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0101","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0101.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-2918","title":"Joomla! Visites 组件 远程文件包含漏洞","description":"Joomla! Visites 组件 1.1 RC2 版本的 core/include/myMailer.class.php 文件存在 PHP 远程文件包含漏洞，攻击者可通过 mosConfig_absolute_path 参数传入恶意 URL，引入并执行任意 PHP 代码。该漏洞影响 Joomla! Visites 1.1 RC2 版本，CVSS 评分 7.5（高危），属于 CWE-94 代码注入类别。攻击者无需认证即可远程利用，通过构造恶意 URL 参数实现远程代码执行，攻击者可完全控制受影响服务器。ExploitDB 已公开该漏洞的利用代码。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2010-2918"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-07-30T20:30:03.847","updated":"2026-06-16T23:21:45.213","remediation":"立即卸载或升级存在漏洞的 Joomla! Visites (com_joomla-visites) 组件 1.1 RC2 至官方修复版本（或移除该组件）；若暂无法升级，可在 php.ini 中设置 allow_url_fopen=Off 与 allow_url_include=Off 禁用远程文件包含，并在 Web 服务器层面使用 .htaccess 限制对 components/com_joomla-visites/ 目录的访问作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://packetstormsecurity.org/0804-exploits/joomlavisites-rfi.txt","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/14476","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/28942","http://www.vupen.com/english/advisories/2010/1925","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/42025","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/14476","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/