证的攻击者仅需发送特制的 HTTP 请求即可利用，无需任何权限或用户交互，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级较高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2010-2682"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-07-12T13:27:28.097","updated":"2026-06-16T23:21:18.330","remediation":"立即升级 Realtyna Translator (com_realtyna) 组件至官方修复版本，或卸载/禁用该组件（Extensions → Manage → Disable）；无法立即升级时，在 Web 应用防火墙或 .htaccess 中拦截 index.php?option=com_realtyna 请求中包含「../」的 controller 参数，并限制 PHP 对网站目录及系统文件的读取权限以缓解任意文件读取风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://packetstormsecurity.org/1004-exploits/joomlarealtyna-lfi.txt","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/14017","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/39337","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/57647","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/14017","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-2682.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0099.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0098","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0098.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-2680","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"inputTokens\":16353,\"outputTokens\":36,\"totalTokens\":16389}}","description":"Joomla! 的 JExtensions JE Section/Property Finder（jesectionfinder）组件存在目录遍历漏洞。该组件在处理 index.php 的 view 参数时未对用户输入进行充分过滤，远程攻击者可在 view 参数中插入 \"../\" 等目录遍历序列，从而包含并执行目标服务器上的任意本地文件。攻击无需身份认证，仅需向受影响站点发送特制的 HTTP 请求即可触发，可导致敏感信息泄露甚至远程代码执行。受影响范围为安装了该缺陷组件的 Joomla! 站点，CVSS 评分 6.8，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.8,"aliases":["CVE-2010-2680"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-07-12T13:27:27.923","updated":"2026-06-16T23:21:15.113","remediation":"建议立即在 Joomla! 后台 Extensions→Manage 中卸载或禁用存在漏洞的 jesectionfinder 组件，该第三方商业扩展官方已不再维护且无安全更新；若必须保留使用，应修补 components/com_jesectionfinder/ 下对 view 参数的处理代码，改用 JInput 获取输入并配合 basename() 或白名单机制仅允许加载预设视图文件，严禁解析含 \"../\" 的目录遍历序列；作为临时缓解，可在 Web 服务器（如 Apache 的 .htaccess 或 Nginx 的 rewrite 规则）中拦截对 /component/jesectionfinder/ 路径中含 \"../\" 或 null 字节的请求。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://packetstormsecurity.org/1006-exploits/joomlajesectionfinder-lfi.txt","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/14064","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/41163","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/59796","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/14064","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-2680.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/2010/CVE-2010-2680.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/6bfef5eb290cbfeb2b2cb4d2bae8e5cab0243137/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-2680.yaml","https://github.com/sepehrdaddev/zap-scripts/blob/2b63b02ca79cc7f0023cdbab72c5c6c774354b07/active/CVE-2010-2680.js","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/b6470123a7d8a7a3e512a294dd5d252afb3fc5a2/CVE-2010/CVE-2010-26xx/CVE-2010-2680.json","https://github.com/0xAwali/Virtual-Host/blob/a2988987751a6ab1f30d71e0d002b7af148c5c79/Templates/CVE/CVE-2010-2680.yaml","https://github.com/ExpLangcn/NucleiTP/blob/2b7ecb9031a6eda4f272793045f29b339d8e0cce/CVES/high/cve-2010-2680-1955.yaml","https://github.com/ARPSyndicate/suricata-vedas/blob/fe24794ad36564b5bbc7c69101525011387b8650/2010/CVE-2010-2680.rules","https://github.com/gongzeq/VAPT3/blob/3576a7accf5cbadc8e64924d6ff48393db379ea7/secbot/resource/poc/cve/cve-2010-2680-1959.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/889686929cb8269a754b7b9536317f741fc92ddc/cves/2010/2xxx/CVE-2010-2680.json","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2010-2680_28.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2010/POC-AVE-2010-0098.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0098.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0096","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0096.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-2307","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"inputTokens\":16403,\"outputTokens\":45,\"totalTokens\":16448}}","description":"Motorola SURFBoard SBV6120E 电缆调制解调器固件 SBV6X2X-1.0.0.5-SCM-02-SHPC 的 Web 服务器存在多个目录遍历漏洞，远程未认证攻击者可通过在 URL 请求中使用多重前导斜杠（//）、点点序列（../）或编码后的点点序列，绕过路径限制读取设备文件系统上的任意文件。该漏洞源于 Web 服务器对用户输入的路径参数缺乏有效规范化与过滤，攻击者无需认证即可远程利用，可导致敏感配置文件、日志文件或系统文件泄露，CVSS 评分 5.0（中危），影响固件版本 SBV6X2X-1.0.0.5-SCM-02-SHPC 的 Motorola SURFBoard SBV6120E 设备。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2010-2307"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-06-16T20:30:02.717","updated":"2026-06-16T23:20:30.680","remediation":"建议联系运营商（ISP）推送或升级 Motorola SURFBoard SBV6120E 至修复该目录遍历漏洞的新版固件（高于受影响的 SBV6X2X-1.0.0.5-SCM-02-SHPC 版本）；过渡期间在边界防火墙或路由器上配置 ACL，禁止从 WAN 侧及公网访问设备管理地址（默认 192.168.100.1 的 80 端口），仅放行受信任的内网主机，并关闭设备不必要的远程 Web 管理功能以阻断 `///`、`../` 及编码形式的任意文件读取。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://secunia.com/advisories/40054","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12865","http://www.osvdb.org/65249","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/40550","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/59113","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12865","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-2307.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/2010/CVE-2010-2307.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/6bfef5eb290cbfeb2b2cb4d2bae8e5cab0243137/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-2307.yaml","https://github.com/sepehrdaddev/zap-scripts/blob/2b63b02ca79cc7f0023cdbab72c5c6c774354b07/active/CVE-2010-2307.js","https://github.com/rix4uni/nucleihub-templates/blob/579a0234551b9e0e322460a62dc77bd6109e4aff/nucleihub-templates/CVE-2010-2307-1943.yaml","https://github.com/0xKayala/Custom-Nuclei-Templates/blob/1940dfd29577590f076c89dec5c30d809d68f210/6001-to-7000-templates/