index.php 传入的 controller 参数时未对用户输入进行充分过滤与校验，攻击者可在参数中插入 \"../\" 序列，突破 Web 根目录限制实现路径穿越。未经身份认证的远程攻击者只需向目标站点发送特制的 HTTP 请求即可读取服务器上的任意文件（如配置文件、敏感数据等），并可能造成其他未明确的影响。该漏洞影响所有使用存在缺陷版本的 Joomla! 站点，CVSS 基础评分 7.5，危害等级为高，攻击条件仅需能访问目标 Web 应用且无需任何权限，利用方式简单、危害显著。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2010-2036"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-05-25T14:30:01.657","updated":"2026-06-16T23:19:51.623","remediation":"卸载废弃的Percha Fields Attach组件，升级到Joomla!5.0+最新版本，确保系统组件仅保留官方维护的扩展包，并通过.htaccess和权限控制禁用文件访问路径，防止其他相同目录遍历漏洞的再次利用。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://packetstormsecurity.org/1005-exploits/joomlaperchafa-lfi.txt","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/40244","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/34004","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-2036.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/2010/CVE-2010-2036.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/6bfef5eb290cbfeb2b2cb4d2bae8e5cab0243137/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-2036.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5df5af06e079a6824349b336150de94d9ba1e7f8/cves/2010/2xxx/CVE-2010-2036.json","https://github.com/0xKayala/Custom-Nuclei-Templates/blob/1940dfd29577590f076c89dec5c30d809d68f210/6001-to-7000-templates/cve-2010-2036-1913.yaml","https://github.com/b1ank1108/VulSentinel/blob/12fae384c4fef6ba595f65eae09dc323d97a95f4/reports/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-2036.md","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2010-2036_29.yaml","https://github.com/Ciyfly/woodpecker/blob/f88bed6da55238547a423ce17dccb2cdbc93be50/pocs/nuclei/cves/2010/CVE-2010-2036.yaml","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_dirtra.txt","https://github.com/ARPSyndicate/suricata-vedas/blob/fe24794ad36564b5bbc7c69101525011387b8650