ases":["CVE-2010-2033"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-05-25T14:30:01.563","updated":"2026-06-16T23:19:51.297","remediation":"升级 Percha Multicategory Article 到 0.8.0 或更高版本，应用 CVE-2010-2033 安全补丁；禁用不必要的路径验证功能；在 web.config 中配置 security.yrewrite=0 并删除组件目录下的.htaccess 文件；使用 W3AF 或 Joomla Sentinel 工具定期扫描目录遍历漏洞；建立日志记录机制，记录所有 controller 参数访问请求。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://packetstormsecurity.org/1005-exploits/joomlaperchact-lfi.txt","http://secunia.com/advisories/39873","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/40244","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/34008","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-2033.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/2010/CVE-2010-2033.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/6bfef5eb290cbfeb2b2cb4d2bae8e5cab0243137/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-2033.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5df5af06e079a6824349b336150de94d9ba1e7f8/cves/2010/2xxx/CVE-2010-2033.json","https://github.com/lianqingsec/NucleiPocGather/blob/dcce204f62196117b9c95c52d8101ccf7a5d27bc/poc/cve/cve-2010-2033-1895.yaml","https://github.com/emadshanab/nucleiDB/blob/a06eb8edf2853662c304e3f41f8887b65f56e399/cve-2010-2033-1897.yaml","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2010-2033_36.yaml","https://github.com/amad3us47/amad3us47.github.io/blob/07cfc0edf465277028554b47198f6f186d3215b6/data/cve-2010-2033-1894.yaml","https://github.com/b1ank1108/VulSentinel/blob/12fae384c4fef6ba595f65eae09dc323d97a95f4/reports/cves.jsonl","https://github.com/cckuailong/reapoc/blob/699762e4c31d0183733f64313d8fc3be6470bd37/2010/README.md","https://github.com/ExpLangcn/NucleiTP/blob/2b7ecb9031a6eda4f272793045f29b339d8e0cce/CVES/high/cve-2010-2033-1898.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0086.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0085","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0085.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-2018","title":"Lokomedia CMS (sukaCMS) 本地文件包含漏洞","description":"Lokomedia CMS (sukaCMS) 1.4.1 和 2.0 版本的 downlot.php 文件存在目录遍历漏洞，远程未认证攻击者可通过 file 参数传入 ../ 目录遍历序列读取服务器任意文件。该漏洞属于路径遍历类型 (CWE-22)，CVSS 评分 5.0 (中危)，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程利用，通过构造恶意文件路径参数即可读取服务器敏感文件如配置文件、密码文件等，导致敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响 Lokomedia CMS 1.4.1 和 2.0 版本，官方已停止维护，建议升级至最新版本或迁移至其他 CMS 系统。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2010-2018"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-05-24T17:30:01.927","updated":"2026-06-16T23:19:49.510","remediation":"建议立即升级到 Lokomedia CMS 2.5.0 或更高版本，该版本修复了 downlot.php 中的目录遍历漏洞，并添加了完整的文件参数验证逻辑。如无法立即升级，可禁用 sisk:// 协议解析功能，并严格限制 file 参数的文件扩展名，仅允许安全的文件类型访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://osvdb.org/64747","http://packetstormsecurity.org/1005-exploits/lokomediacms-disclose.txt","http://secunia.com/advisories/39863","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12651","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/58670","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12651","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-2018.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/2010/CVE-2010-2018.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/6bfef5eb290cbfeb2b2cb4d2bae8e5cab0243137/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-2018.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5df5af06e079a6824349b336150de94d9ba1e7f8/cves/2010/2xxx/CVE-2010-2018.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2010/CVE-2010-2018","https://github.com/ARPSyndicate/suricata-vedas/blob/fe24794ad36564b5bbc7c69101525011387b8650/2010/CVE-2010-2018.rules","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/6593a7cdb3db460855b778a366e9ba479f28af94/CVE/data/2010/CVE-2010-2018.json","https://github.c